text:
This ended up being bigger that I thought...
If this needs splitting up into smaller chunks then let me know!

ast_objects.inv contains the [Green Tree Snakes](http://greentreesnakes.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) documentation inventory, but with the classes prepended with `ast` so that they don't conflict with astroid nodes and therefore we can still link to `ast` documentation.
